A student writes the following CB pseudocode to find the largest number in a list:

PROCEDURE findMax(numList)
{
  max ← numList[1]
  FOR EACH item IN numList
  {
    IF(item > max)
    {
      max ← item
    }
  }
  RETURN(max)
}

What does findMax([4, 7, 2, 9, 5]) return?
